code: /**  * Returns if the underlying operation is blocking.  * @return {@code true} if the operation is blocking  */ boolean isBlocking().

code: /**  * Returns the predicate for requests that can be handled by this operation.  * @return the predicate  */ WebOperationRequestPredicate getRequestPredicate().
